{"tid":413414,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有乜理由上個論壇都要比錢，打機睇電視都免費做到啦","createTime":"2017-09-25T12:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T15:36:37.000Z","uid":4512,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2eebf73d385db38c769b849c83092e48b9e77fa0","tid":413414,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老味</span><br />\n<br />\n就係「免費」呢啲on9觀念搞到今時今日越來越多野既質素都下跌。回想以前online game 一開始隻隻都要月費，但收得你錢都叫搞得個game 好玩，後來開左先河免費玩，啲online game 質素就越來越差，個個開發商只係諗點樣邋一筆就走人。<br />\n<br />\n打機係咁，資訊又係咁，好多高質傳媒其實要收錢先圍到皮，但個個都覺得資訊應該係「免費」，結果我地得番啲01, cctvb , 劣幣驅逐良幣。<br />\n<br />\n製造好既內容就應該有人欣賞，有適當既回報，而錢就係最直接既support。依家香港人成日比地產霸權壓拃，但係自己有機會嘅時候就走去壓拃返人哋。所有創意產業、IT、創作，都係唔值錢嘅，應該乞食嘅。淨係飲飲食食、供樓先值得俾錢。黃子華講魚蛋論真係啱。<br />\n<br />\n今次個計劃豐儉由人，冇話要你一定俾錢先可以留言開post，唔想比咪望下啲廣告囉，屌人收嗰少少錢真係好低質。"},{"pid":"04ff64c187d589d4f80e54cbd6530f7e69b61235","tid":413414,"uid":90863,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"打咁多字把撚<br />\n「香港人正乞兒」，搞掂"},{"pid":"bf69b254d4e9cc48fc856380b2c671007b3bff8e","tid":413414,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咁多字把撚<br />\n「香港人正乞兒」，搞掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔想踩自己人，但真係太貪小便宜 小聰明"},{"pid":"7f87c7fb1616cb949023ea17616236ef7b8259e1","tid":413414,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"窮就出聲啦"},{"pid":"1a6b7fef316eb5156ddba28c3852ffe2f8f352c3","tid":413414,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"可能得你一個想高質<br />\n以為自己好醒"},{"pid":"ff1adfdb1298151e0d8733dc870ad8ed44768469","tid":413414,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36ace83ed3115ebbabb25fc5c55fcadad34a379","tid":413414,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果有app內購買<br />\n都考慮支持"},{"pid":"e249835f56f5abb1ec82c62d68827d7959f304a2","tid":413414,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382cd09c12892d64dcd9898cacbd74da04ab644e","tid":413414,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}